data.description: Discover the warmth and comfort of this charming single-level home in Rancho Verde Estates! Providing 4 beds, 2 baths, and a 2-car garage. Inside, you'll find a desirable open layout design for effortless entertaining. Vaulted ceilings enhance the airy feel, complemented by bountiful natural light throughout. The kitchen offers built-in appliances, wood cabinetry, a pantry, and a 2-tiered island w/breakfast bar. Large main bedroom boasts an ensuite with a separate tub/shower, dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Out the back, you have a grassy area and covered & open patios - a perfect spot to relax or enjoy BBQ. If you are looking for a project, this property is the one! It has great bones & just needs a little TLC. Close to schools, parks, dining, shopping, and freeways. Don't miss this gem!
